data.description: Immaculate 5 bedroom 2 story Georgian on a half acre lot! The main floor has real oak hardwood floors. A large family room offers a fireplace with marble accents & custom mantle.  French doors lead to the living room.  Private office on the first floor. A generous-sized kitchen has custom oak cabinets granite countertops and a walk-in pantry. The backyard has beautifully mature trees, a deck, a shed, and a garden for the summer months.  This is one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. The fully finished basement has a 5th bedroom, family room, workout room, a large storage area, and a backup battery for the sump pump. The main floor powder and the upstairs bathroom have been completely remodeled. A large 2.5-car garage and backyard shed offer plenty of storage.
